36
00:01:49.833 --> 00:01:51.167
No!

37
00:01:51.208 --> 00:01:53.042
Marie Curie!

38
00:01:53.083 --> 00:01:54.042
This is boring!

39
00:01:54.083 --> 00:01:56.542
Can we talk about
sex ed or something?

40
00:01:56.583 --> 00:01:57.917
[bell ringing]

41
