86
00:05:06.750 --> 00:05:08.500
See ya!

87
00:05:08.542 --> 00:05:10.417
Don't try it.

88
00:05:10.458 --> 00:05:12.750
Cute bird's nest.

89
00:05:12.792 --> 00:05:15.000
