167
00:08:32.875 --> 00:08:34.292
♪ Gotta get
the heck outta here... ♪

168
00:08:34.333 --> 00:08:37.083
Hey! Looks like
I'm your new neighbour.

169
00:08:38.958 --> 00:08:40.292
Okay.

170
00:08:44.042 --> 00:08:45.250
[spits]

171
00:08:45.292 --> 00:08:49.250
♪ Gotta go. gotta get
the heck outta here... ♪

172
00:09:01.792 --> 00:09:03.167
