Happy birthday to me.

218
00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:50.875
Ah!
You must be. um. Coach Chuck!

219
00:10:50.917 --> 00:10:52.083
Hey. man.

220
00:10:52.125 --> 00:10:54.125
